

=Description=

"Introducing e-enabled citizens’ panels: E-panel software was identified and evaluated from three organisations: Community People, iNovem and the Practical eDemocracy in London project. A fourth identified software provider, BMG, felt unable to participate at this stage. Full details of this evaluation are available in the software evaluation report. The three software packages were then piloted from January/February 2005."
